title: UGREEN 3.5mm to 2RCA Audio Auxiliary Stereo Y Splitter Cable (6ft)

This high-end 3.5mm to 2RCA stereo adapter cables offer incredible audio clarity over all lengths to provide a versatile connection between hardware for all your stereo audio needs.

Broad Compatibility: This 3.5mm to 2RCA Audio Auxiliary Stereo Y Splitter Cable is compatible with iPhone, iPod, iPad, tablets including Google Nexus, Samsung, MP3 players, CD players, laptops, tablets and any other digital device with a 3.5mm audio jack; and home audio systems, like amplifier or receiver with RCA(white/left and red/right sockets)jacks.
Fantastic Audio Quality: Gold Plated connectors and oxygen-free copper provide maximum's conductivity and durability, ensuring optimal stereo audio transmission.

Slim 3.5mm Connector: With very slim connector, 3.5mm tablet/MP3/iPhone to 2RCA receiver/speaker could accommodate most mobile devices in a aslim case with a snug and secure connection. No need to take off your slim protective cases for smartphone, tablets.
